OL,3,CTitanic submersible widow says
OL,4,Cimplosion was 'best of all worst-case
OL,5,Cscenarios'
OL,7,FChristina Dawood was the Titan support
OL,8,Fship when the submersible imploded,
OL,9,FGood Morning Britain reports
OL,11,FThe wife and mother of two men who
OL,12,Fdied on the Titan submersible three
OL,13,Fyears ago has said its implosion was
OL,14,F"the best of all worst-case scenarios"
OL,15,Fin a new memoir.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
