CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778529954
OL,3,CTitanic submersible widow says
OL,4,Cimplosion was 'best of all worst-case
OL,5,Cscenarios'
OL,7,FFather and son, Shahzada and Suleman
OL,8,FDawood, died alongside Hamish Harding,
OL,9,FPaul-Henri Nargeolet and OceanGate CEO
OL,10,FStockton Rush when the Titan imploded
OL,11,Fduring a dive to see the Titanic in
OL,12,FJune 2023.
OL,14,FNow, Christina Dawood has written a
OL,15,Fmemoir, Ninety-Six Hours, documenting
OL,16,Fher experience aboard the Titan's
OL,17,Fsupport vessel, the Polar Prince,
OL,18,Fwhere she waited with her daughter as
OL,19,Fthe submersible made its final dive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778529954
OL,3,CTitanic submersible widow says
OL,4,Cimplosion was 'best of all worst-case
OL,5,Cscenarios'
OL,7,FFor 96 hours, the estimated amount of
OL,8,Foxygen the submersible had left, she
OL,9,Fheld on to hope that Shahzada and
OL,10,FSuleman could be rescued, not knowing
OL,11,Fthey had already died.
OL,13,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain on
OL,14,FMonday, Dawood said the implosion was
OL,15,Fthe best-case scenario "because they
OL,16,Fdidn't have to suffer".
OL,18,F"The brain didn't even recognise and
OL,19,Fthey were gone before the brain would
OL,20,Feven have been able to recognise (they
OL,21,Fwere dead)," she said.
OL,26,@|D@bpm}D@Jpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778529954
OL,3,CTitanic submersible widow says
OL,4,Cimplosion was 'best of all worst-case
OL,5,Cscenarios'
OL,7,F"Because the thought of them slowly
OL,8,Fsuffocating? That would have been... I
OL,9,Fthink I would be in a very different
OL,10,Fplace right now."
OL,12,FChristina also said she was not
OL,13,F"angry" at OceanGate, despite a US
OL,14,FCoast Guard investigation concluding
OL,15,Fthat the company's design and testing
OL,16,Fprocesses were "critically flawed" and
OL,17,Fthe implosion was "preventable."
OL,19,FThe report also suggested that had
OL,20,FRush survived, he could have faced
OL,21,Fcriminal charges for negligence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778529954
OL,3,CTitanic submersible widow says
OL,4,Cimplosion was 'best of all worst-case
OL,5,Cscenarios'
OL,7,F"What would the anger serve? So anger
OL,8,Fis part of grief. I mean, if you go
OL,9,Fthrough the grief cycle, anger is part
OL,10,Fof it," Christina said.
OL,12,FThe report also said OceanGate had a
OL,13,F"toxic workplace environment" and used
OL,14,Fthe "looming threat of being fired" to
OL,15,Fprevent staff from coming forward with
OL,16,Fsafety concerns
OL,18,F"But I don't want to get stuck in it
OL,19,Fbecause it's a part of a whole circle
OL,20,Fwhere you have to move on, and it's
OL,21,Fnot good for me."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778529954
OL,3,CTitanic submersible widow says
OL,4,Cimplosion was 'best of all worst-case
OL,5,Cscenarios'
OL,7,FShe added: "There are moments where
OL,8,FI'm angry, yes, at the world, at
OL,9,Fmyself and, you know, at anything. But
OL,10,FI don't want to reside in that anger
OL,11,Fbecause there's so much I can still do
OL,12,Fto help others.
OL,14,F"There are other people to live for.
OL,15,FAnd if I'm in this bitter and angry
OL,16,Fphase, then people will stop talking."
OL,18,FNinety-Six Hours will be published on
OL,19,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
